#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc234"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts234"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.6:5.1"
msgid "“Ye cittakathī bahussutā,"
msgstr "“One of those monks who live in Pāṭaliputta—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.6:5.2"
msgid "Samaṇā pāṭaliputtavāsino;"
msgstr "Such brilliant speakers, and very learned—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.6:5.3"
msgid "Tesaññataroyamāyuvā,"
msgstr "Stands at the door:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.6:5.4"
msgid "Dvāre tiṭṭhati khujjasobhito”."
msgstr "The old man, Khujjasobhita."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc235"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts235"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.6:6.1"
msgid "“Ye cittakathī bahussutā,"
msgstr "One of those monks who live in Pāṭaliputta—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.6:6.2"
msgid "Samaṇā pāṭaliputtavāsino;"
msgstr "Such brilliant speakers, and very learned—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.6:6.3"
msgid "Tesaññataroyamāyuvā,"
msgstr "Stands at the door:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.6:6.4"
msgid "Dvāre tiṭṭhati māluterito”."
msgstr "An old man, trembling in the wind.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc236"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts236"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.6:7.1"
msgid "“Suyuddhena suyiṭṭhena,"
msgstr "“By war well fought, by sacrifice well made,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.6:7.2"
msgid "saṅgāmavijayena ca;"
msgstr "By victory in battle;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.6:7.3"
msgid "Brahmacariyānuciṇṇena,"
msgstr "By living the spiritual life:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.6:7.4"
msgid "evāyaṃ sukhamedhatī”ti."
msgstr "That’s how this person prospers in happiness.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
